;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	1、9月8日中午12时至9月9日中午12时间，随手拍下你当时当地月亮的照片（也可以是合照），附上所在省市，微信发送给“环保圈”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2、每位活动参与者都将获得参与奖一份\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	3、9月9日-9月12日中午12时截止，对所收到的照片进行微信投票。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	4、得票最高的前三位分别获得一、二、三等奖\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	也许你会说“看人家上千元的中秋送礼多么豪气”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:1.5;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;但你不知道的是中奖的几率已经被他调成了0&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:1.5;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;也许你会说“网上盗个图发过来不久好了么”&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:1.5;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;但你不知道的是度娘有个识图功能，盗版原创一看便知，调戏小编是不可取滴&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453880048', '0', '', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('20', '2', '17', '中国环博会·固废展助力垃圾处理行业迎接下一春', '9', '&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	随着城镇化建设进程的发展，城镇生活垃圾处理面临巨大挑战。据预测，“十二五”期间，我国环保产业投资规模将达到3.1万亿元，其中固体废物处理行业将达到8000亿元，全国城镇生活垃圾无害化处理设施建设总投资约2636亿元，工业固体废物资源化的产业规模有望达到1200亿元，固体废物处理产业成为环保行业的后起之秀。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	中国环博会·固废展，作为国内唯一完整呈现固体废弃物处理、回收和再利用整条产业链的展览会，秉承世界第一环保展IFAT优秀品质，已经成为产业最为优秀的技术交流、设备展示平台。第十六届中国环博会·固废展将于2015年5月6-8日在上海新国际博览中心举办。本次展会将协同国家重量级官方机构，更多数量的全球领先企业，多元化互动交流形式，打造覆盖固废处理全产业链的最热交流平台！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;领先企业抢占优势之地&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	一年一届的中国环博会·固废展已经成为固废处理产业专业人士翘首以盼的必选盛会，展位开始销售至今短短2个月内，固废展专馆售出面积已达5000平米，包括TITECH中国、申嘉三和、嘉诺集团、施德耐特、艺利磁铁、埃维恩、BHS、联冠集团、凯天环保、百利阳光、虎牌、拉斯卡、汉意塑料机械、奥美森等在内的一大批垃圾处理与回收利用、垃圾处理成套设备、废弃物综合利用与发电领域的龙头企业争先恐后，纷纷抢驻占领固废展专馆要地。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;“展+会”模式打造最热交流平台&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:24pt;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	展+会的互动模式是中国环博会的核心优势。2014年展会同期举办的国际固体废弃物处理与资源回收高峰论坛，凭借其重量级演讲嘉宾、权威的组织机构、全面的行业议题获得业内人士的推崇。2015年国际固废产业高峰论坛将秉持自身优势，贴近市场拓展议题，广邀海内外行业专家、业内主管部门、科研院所带头人、及领头企业参与论坛，更有多层面、强有力的合作伙伴的支持，保证政府和工业用户的大量参与。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453881307', '0', '', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('21', '2', '17', '陈善坤：关注城乡一体化 建设净化、美化新广东', '9', '&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2015年11月9日，广东省环境卫生协会(以下简称省环卫协会)迎来了25周岁生日。成立25年来，协会充分发挥桥梁纽带作用，服务政府、服务会员、服务行业，在建立全省环卫行业交流平台，搭建与各级政府之间、政府和企业之间沟通桥梁等方面做了大量卓有成效的工作。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	据悉，2015年9月25日，经广东省第十二届人民代表大会常务委员会第二十次会议审议通过，全国首个省级城乡生活垃圾管理条例——《广东省城乡生活垃圾处理条例》将自2016年1月1日起正式施行。从2013年开始，广东省就着手开展了新条例的起草工作，并由省环卫协会负责条例起草，先后经过修改、调整、征求公众意见，再修改、再调整，耗时将近2年完成。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	在广东省环境卫生协会二十五周年庆典暨国际固废与资源回收利用高峰论坛上，省环卫协会陈善坤会长向北极星节能环保网表示，《广东省城乡生活垃圾处理条例》作为全国首个省级城乡生活垃圾管理条例，不仅仅将农村生活垃圾管理纳入了新条例内容，还结合新时期新形势下推进生活垃圾分类的工作要求做了详细规定。明确了城乡生活垃圾管理主体、生活垃圾分类类别，规定了生活垃圾分类管理实行管理责任人制度，并明确了责任人的具体工作责任。规定了农村生活垃圾处理的责任主体和农村生活垃圾处理方式，要求推行农村生活垃圾分类处理。条例还规定了城乡环卫规划编制程序，对生活垃圾收集点、垃圾转运站等设施的建设也提出了明确要求。条例还提出了建立生活垃圾处理运营单位信用体系和失信惩戒机制、黑名单制度。新条例的颁布实施，又将推动广东环卫进入新的历史发展时期。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	陈会长提到，“广东的环卫工作之所以走在全国的前列主要是因为广东的环卫基础设施建设起步比较早，起点较高，运营管理较规范。我们下一步的工作重点是拉近粤东西北和珠三角的差距。粤东西北因为经济发展的原因，在垃圾处理方面暂时落后于珠三角。但他们正在迎头赶上。起步虽晚，建设水平和运营标准不会低。我希望整个广东省的垃圾处理以及运营管理水平继续领先全国。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	在提及“十三五”广东省环卫工作的重点时。陈会长明确指出：“下一步，我们将集中力量推动农村垃圾整治，也就是说要整县推进垃圾处理。按照广东省政府和省住建厅的要求，广东省环境卫生协会将推出一系列活动，比如专家企业家携手走乡村活动，为的是让专家和企业家一起下基层，走到农村，帮助村委会、镇、县相关部门，推动农村垃圾治理。真正实现‘美丽乡村，宜居生活’。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	在访问中陈会长还提到：“‘十二五’期间广东省所有垃圾处理设施建设基本完成，将进入运营管理阶段。‘十三五’我们将重点工作放在县级以下农村垃圾的整治。将农村垃圾处理逐步纳入规范化管理，减少垃圾污染，创造美好宜居环境。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	未来的广东，将处处呈现“净化、美化的宜居环境”。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453881341', '0', '', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('22', '2', '17', '中国环博会沪穗双城闪耀，助力十三五创新绿色发展', '9', '&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2016年是“十三五”规划的开局之年，绿色成为五年规划的主色调。美丽中国首次写入五年规划，环保升至国家战略高度。“十三五”规划建议中用空前篇幅部署环保工作，顶层设计及相关配套方案如“土十条”等即将登台，将持续提升环保产业的内涵和扩大发展的外延。未来五年环保投资预计高达17万亿，环保产业进入更快发展的大好时期。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;近日，德国慕尼黑博览集团及中贸慕尼黑展览（上海）有限公司对外宣布，为顺应国家坚定不移发展绿色经济的战略，全球最大环保展慕尼黑环博会IFAT中国展—中国环博会，将每年在上海及广州两个城市举办，形成“一年两地、沪穗双展”的新局面，助力“十三五”开局之年全面打响环境污染防治攻坚战。&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;据悉，第十七届中国环博会将于2016年5月5-7日在上海新国际博览中心举办，展示规模将扩大至80,000平米。今年11月首次进军华南举办的“广州环博会”也正式加入IFAT全球展大家庭，更名为“中国环博会广州展”，并将于2016年11月24-26日在广交会琶洲展馆再度拉开帷幕。&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	由中国环境科学学会、慕尼黑博览集团、全联环境服务业商会、中贸慕尼黑展览等倾心打造的中国环博会，自2000年伊始，扎根中国环保产业16年，每年一届在上海举办，被誉为亚洲第一的环保交流盛会。主办方胡总监表示，目前国家经济下行压力不断加大，创新及绿色经济成为经济发展的新动能。2016中国环博会以“绿色科技”及“创新”为核心，沪、穗两地双展联动，升级打造亚洲环保交流平台2.0，助力企业抢滩“十三五”巨大环保红利。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	中国环博会上海展以“绿色科技”为核心，在水、固废、大气、土壤四大专题展的基础上，新增农村废弃物治理及环境监测检测仪器等特色展区，集中展示全球市政、工业、农村环境污染治理创新科技。同时利用IFAT全球资源，联合如环保部固体废物与化学品管理技术中心、上海市环境科学研究院、国家污泥处理处置产业技术创新战略联盟、德国水、污水和废弃物处理协会等百余家权威组织机构，聚焦“十三五”环保规划，重幅打造“中国环博会高峰论坛”及“国际创新环境技术投资洽谈会”，丰富环保技术交流议题及外延，加强环保领域政、产、学、研之间的互通。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	与此同时，中国环博会广州展以“创新创业”为主题，秉承慕尼黑环博会及中国环博会长久的卓越品质及品牌影响力，2015年首秀展出面积达10,000平米，共有13个国家和地区的201展商同台亮相，吸引专业观众15,148人次。展会获得了广东省环保厅及各界参与者的赞赏及肯定。2016年中国环博会广州展整体规模将扩大至25,000平方米，同期举办的创新创业大会下设数十场高品质论坛交流会、技能比赛与培训等，为混乱的华南环保展会市场，带来一个覆盖环保全产业链可持续的品牌宣传、技术交流平台。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453881364', '0', '', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('23', '2', '17', '环保圈年度巨献，中国环博会广州展重磅升级归来！', '9', '&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;文章导读：&lt;/strong&gt;转眼又到了辞旧迎新之际，环保圈也迎来“大事记”。2016广州国际环保展览会暨创新创业大会（简称：中国环博会广州展）项目宣布正式启动， 启动仪式上项目总监对项目进行了全新的解读，提出了本届展会新的计划与要求，致力为环保行业提供一场环保饕餮盛宴，打造华南环保展新势力！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://guangzhou.ie-expo.cn/files/conference/we.jpg&quot; style=&quot;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:500px;height:418px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://guangzhou.ie-expo.cn/files/conference/we1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:500px;height:418px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2015年，中国环博会联手行业强力机构，首次进军华南环保市场，打造泛珠三角区域最高品质环保展“2015广州环博会”。首秀展出面积达10,000平米，共有13个国家和地区的201展商同台亮相，共吸引专业观众15,148人次，效果非同凡响；&lt;strong&gt;2016年，中国环博会广州展正式加入“IFAT全球系列”大家庭，共享全球宣传资源，为环保从业者打造更高品质华南区域环保展。&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2016中国环博会广州展以“技术创新，促进绿色未来”为主旨，集中展示创新的水与污水处理、给水排水、固废处理、大气治理、场地修复的技术与设备，同期举办“中国环博会创新创业大会”，下设数十场丰富且紧扣行业热点的专业论坛与活动，与产业链各端精英一同把握行业动向，探讨创新解决方案。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;新新新！品牌升级-新年就该有新气象&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2016中国环博会广州展不止在名称上有了新变化，在整个视觉感官上也做出了相应的新改变：\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:14px;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;新logo：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;2016中国环博会广州展开始采用新Logo标识，新logo标识与上海展保持一致，正式成IFAT中国展一员\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://guangzhou.ie-expo.cn/files/conference/we2.jpg&quot; style=&quot;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:500px;height:250px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:14px;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;新色调：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;2016中国环博会广州展结合了天空蓝与大地青作为展会VI的主色调，象征着干净、自然与纯粹，给予广州展助力改变亚洲乃至世界环境的美好期望。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://guangzhou.ie-expo.cn/files/conference/we4.jpg&quot; style=&quot;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:500px;height:275px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:14px;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;新网站：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;2016中国环博会广州展官网也进行了全新的改版，更新了网站的域名&lt;strong&gt;（新网站为：&lt;a href=&quot;http://gz.ie-expo.cn/&quot; style=&quot;border:0px;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-decoration:none;&quot;&gt;http://gz.ie-expo.cn/&lt;/a&gt;）&lt;/strong&gt;、色调，使得新网站的颜色与VI色调保持一致，充分提高了中国环博会广州展的辨识度。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://guangzhou.ie-expo.cn/files/conference/we5.png&quot; style=&quot;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:500px;height:290px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;优优优！展会服务全面优化！&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2016年中国环博会广州展继承了2015年广州国际环保展览会的优势，从展馆布局，展商分类，观众质量等方面对2016年中国环博会广州展进行全面升级，&lt;strong&gt;真正的做到了与“IFAT全球系列展”资源上无缝共享。&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2016年中国环博会广州展将扩大展出范围，提高展商数量，并对展区分布进行更为合理的安排，提高观众观展舒适度便捷度，也提高展商之间信息交流的专业度、有效度。另外，&lt;strong&gt;将加大对专业观众的邀约，增加终端用户观展，并加大对东南亚地区海外观众的邀约，提升了广州展的国际化程度。&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;border:0px;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:24px;font-family:微软雅黑, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Arial;vertical-align:baseline;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;text-indent:2em;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2016年中国环博会广州展将以华南为中心，与西南，华东互为犄角，带动港澳台，辐射亚洲的所有参展企业及采购商，&lt;strong&gt;旨在加强和推进中国环保行业的发展，为中高端专业人士，提供解决方案的一站式采购贸易平台。&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453881387', '0', '', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('24', '2', '17', '环保企业家沙龙热情洋溢，90后创业引情怀', '5', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;在第16届中国环博会召开之际，中国环博会沙龙也将顺势举办了第七期活动。本次沙龙以“企业家之夜”为主题，邀请到9位环保企业家和环保人士，以对话的形式，回顾企业摸爬滚打的过往十年，分享环保新转型的机遇与挑战，探讨企业跨进或走出国门的经验。期间，会场最年轻的90后环保企业家的一番创业宣言，引起在场多数大佬内心的怀旧和救世情怀。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96Ls4yWka707cecNlPZ9oajfkicotdQU0Xm2lzm1aGNbASb27LcSKxqx2zA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.66600790513834&quot; data-w=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96Ls4yWka707cecNlPZ9oajfkicotdQU0Xm2lzm1aGNbASb27LcSKxqx2zA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; i2s_selected=&quot;true&quot; i2s_guid=&quot;de2afd04-0bc4-6f65-e357-0f277c9e65d6&quot; i2s_id=&quot;1ee02d2ccf67fbfcac2ffded16db8436&quot; i2s_untagged=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;企业的十年也是中国环保的十年&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;width:480.68px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;凯天环保科技股份有限公司董事长叶明强认为，近十年的环保产业变化主要在于两个方面：市场和技术。国内对工厂环境内的污染问题重视度逐渐增强，市场需求由之前的卖方需求转变为买方市场。在技术方面，从国外引进到如今的自主研发。众多企业已经拥有核心技术或是针对不同领域技术特点。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;就这十年的环保局势变化，联合环境技术有限公司首席技术官刘建林表示，机遇大于挑战。首先大众对环境污染的认识水平提高。其次，历史遗留的环境问题到了该治理的时候。最后是政府加强对环境监管的政策，在投资方面和资金的来源方面也有了观念的转变，给专业的环保公司提供市场。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;安尼康（福建）环保设备有限公司总经理郑朝志讲述了初入中国市场面临众多山寨品低价格的市场窘境，对如何度过企业困难期发表看法。他认为价格是重要的竞争条件之一，在不断技术创新的同时，能够缩小价格差距，就能在市场稳固占有率。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96LsbibM8a4IStgDcxQLhTwfLwPVD7w7ZM2NJ4p3uf9Jq0pS29ibyByoqpEw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.66600790513834&quot; data-w=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96LsbibM8a4IStgDcxQLhTwfLwPVD7w7ZM2NJ4p3uf9Jq0pS29ibyByoqpEw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; i2s_selected=&quot;true&quot; i2s_guid=&quot;12141b8f-8077-f9b8-c21b-fc03ecf19a18&quot; i2s_id=&quot;29f07e113318a14f550850cc99c9bd13&quot; i2s_untagged=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;从商业模式到体制改革，转型发展更强劲&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;width:480.68px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;北京泰昌科睿环保科技有限公司的转型，主要由商业模式的成型及业务领域多元化的扩展组成。其董事长孔丽娜提出市场的重要性，仅仅有技术是不够的，需要资本运作与经营，这不仅仅是大型企业的玩物，中小型企业也可以拥有，只要能够抱团取暖，就能照亮一片天空。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;中海油安全技术服务有限公司科技经理孟庭宇表示通过资源整合，该企业从人力资源转型做安全环保产业，此外还进行系统外和海外市场的拓展及股份制的改制。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;大连利浦环境能源工程技术有限公司是经营思维的转变。从总经理刘程格外强调“专注”二字。专注产品的制造和服务，提高能效。达到短期少花钱，远期更挣钱的目的。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96LsgNuPEsauKUlvvqwtvrgJ7O29NFZ7h1Q0LWDnqqKTnJR7UMnGct4pMA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.66600790513834&quot; data-w=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96LsgNuPEsauKUlvvqwtvrgJ7O29NFZ7h1Q0LWDnqqKTnJR7UMnGct4pMA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; i2s_selected=&quot;true&quot; i2s_guid=&quot;eaf44201-ee07-f956-71a5-c9813462c28f&quot; i2s_id=&quot;7c7e889e1d5b2c3466761425104d8f4e&quot; i2s_untagged=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;本土化和拒绝本土化&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;width:480.68px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;德国瑞曼迪斯公司副董事长谢炜分享公司历程，厚积而薄发。花12年时间潜伏，看中市场后全力以赴。目标成为中国最大的综合利用工业固废的运营商总结出独占未必鳌头，合作必定双赢。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;作为海归的环保人士，杭州碧清环保科技有限公司董事长夏抒向在场嘉宾传达清洁企业原则。创造一个全新的生态链，与大学研究机构以及政府进行合作，通过这个模式把技术介绍到中国。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;在国内外环保行业的差异问题上，柏美迪康环保科技上海有限公司总经理徐潜，给出了他的答案：国外的理念是基于一个清洁的环境中形成的，与国内的环境不同。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96LsicAib4zpJDbkWo4aJOJkrIibjruxLQ4RV5qnspLCbVJ6QhFvjr3vkHgGw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.66600790513834&quot; data-w=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Ke0bgSnVX5FiaqzwaNRvyqicRT3Pwj96LsicAib4zpJDbkWo4aJOJkrIibjruxLQ4RV5qnspLCbVJ6QhFvjr3vkHgGw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; i2s_selected=&quot;true&quot; i2s_guid=&quot;3892bd49-5c49-1255-acee-bfa47ba7e49b&quot; i2s_id=&quot;81d1dd6d55d07b2a666916a971971132&quot; i2s_untagged=&quot;true&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;width:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;90后创业引情怀&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;作为到场嘉宾中的一位&lt;/span&gt;90&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;后企业家，巩义市绿洁环保材料有限公司总经理李彦东的发言得到了众多企业家的积极回应。包括瑞曼迪斯的副董事在内的几位大佬纷纷表示从创业者的身上看到了当初的自己。徐潜总经理更是肯定了90后的勇于挑战权威，将成为未来环保产业技术创新改革的主人公。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453907385', '1453909101', '/uploads/17/article/0000000001.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('25', '2', '17', '环保重压下纺织染整业的未来之路：困境与变革', '9', '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:28px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.75em;\">纺织业是当之无愧的工业耗水大户，同时他的废水排放量与污染力也惊人。在工业用水水价不断上升的同时，纺织染整业排污门槛再一次提升。2015年1月1日新修订的《环保法》正式实施，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.75em;letter-spacing:0px;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">伴随发布两年《纺织染整工业水污染物排放标准》也正式全面执行，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.75em;\">“现有企业”的过渡期结束，开始执行与“新建企业”同样严格的排放标准，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.75em;letter-spacing:0px;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">国内印染企业排污标准也越来越严苛。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">“过渡期”余音散尽，企业是否能达到排放标准？</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">为达到标准，需要投入大量资金，企业该如何权衡？</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">满足新标准需要新建更多的处理设施，受征地指标或工业园规划的限制，土地空间不足怎么办？</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">目前许多园区施行废水“集中预处理”，由于公共污水处理系统无法消化，造成“集中污染”的现象。纳管企业是否应该承担间接排放责任？</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">面临水价与环保双重尴尬，纺织企业该何去何从？</span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:28px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75em;text-indent:28px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">中国环博会将联合</span>苏州市环境保护产业协会、苏州高新区、虎丘区环境保护产业协会，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.75em;\">在苏州主办第六届中国环博会沙龙。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;line-height:1.75em;\">纺织染整企业及工业废水处理企业齐聚一堂，特别<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">邀请全国五一劳动奖章获得者</span><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">高级工程师陈茂林先生。</strong>本次沙龙以“环保重压下纺织染整业的未来之路：困境与变革”为主题，一起深入探析《纺织染整工业水污染物排放标准》对纺织、印染企业带来的影响以及解决方法。</span> \r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453909145', '0', '/uploads/17/article/0000000002.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('26', '2', '17', '新《环保法》实施，政府、执法人员、企业亚历山大', '10', '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	本次沙龙借迎新之际，邀请到上海市环保局环保执法大队周副总队长，上海政法学院环境资源法学科负责人王教授，组织工业污染企业及环保企业齐聚一堂，以“新《环保法》研读会”为主题，共同解析新《环保法》的主要条款和亮点与过去旧法的差异，及新《环保法》实施后对环保企业及污染企业的影响。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;text-indent:32px;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:5px 0px 13px;padding:0px 10px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;border-width:0px 0px 0px 5px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#E96363;font-family:微软雅黑;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;color:#E96363;line-height:25px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">沙龙概况</strong> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">活动主题</strong>：新《环保法》研读会\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">特邀分享嘉宾：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	上海市环保局环保执法大队副总队长 周浒\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	上海政法学院教授 环境资源法学科负责人 王文革\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">主办单位：</strong>中国环博会\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">参与人数：</strong>32人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:5px 0px 13px;padding:0px 10px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;border-width:0px 0px 0px 5px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#E96363;font-family:微软雅黑;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;color:#E96363;line-height:25px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">亮点回顾</strong> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	1、目前总体环保形势是局部有所改善，总体恶化，形势不容乐观。全国地面水和地下水污染程度相当严重，雾霾的浓度和频率越来越高，违法处置危废的犯罪行为最多。在此背景下催生的新《环保法》，一定是非常严格的，但是越是严格的法律，执行性难度越大。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	2、新法首先调整了与发展的关系，原法是“环保与发展相协调”，而新法是“发展与环保相协调”，这表明了环保将从被动地位变为主动的地位。新法讲究保护优先、预防为主、综合治理、公众参与、损害担责的原则，且必须违法成本高于守法成本。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	3、新《环保法》将成为史上最严的环保法，政府、执法人员和企业都将面临各种挑战：\r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;list-style-type:square;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">对政府严</strong>——各个地区的环境质量跟人口结构、能源结构 、产业结构相关，三种结构调整与政府有关，所以新法指出各级政府（从正级）对当地环境质量负责，\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">对执法人员严</strong>——在九种情形下，环保执法人员如不履行职责，轻则行政处分，重则移交司法\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">对企业严</strong>——按日计罚、限产停产、查封扣押、行政拘留、双罚制度，五项措施严格执行好之后，行程“违法成本高、执法成本高、守法成本低”的两高一低现象。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	4、行政拘留适用400多种环境违法行为，其中以下三种违法行为最为常见：\r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;list-style-type:square;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			利用私设暗管排放废水或者利用渗坑渗井排放一般污染物\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			篡改伪造在线监测数据\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			未经环境审批先建的项目，取消补办环评，责令停止建设，可以直接处以罚款，可以责令回复原状，拒不整改的可以移交公安机关处以行政拘留\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	5、上海自2015年1月1日起，对二氧化硫、氮氧化物、化学需氧量和氨氮4项主要污染物提高排污收费标准，由1.2-1.3元/公斤提到3-4元/公斤，到2019年。如果减排会有减收，如果超标就会加倍收费。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:5px 0px 13px;padding:0px 10px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;border-width:0px 0px 0px 5px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-color:#E96363;font-family:微软雅黑;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;color:#E96363;line-height:25px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">不同观点</strong> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	1、<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">企业总量控制排放的指标是根据什么来确定？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	总量都是国家分给政府，政府分给企业。各环保局总量处汇总企业的排放现状上报后，国家再按照制度分解下来。但是目前企业上报的数据是包含很大的水分的，要非常科学的统计总量是非常难的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">2、关于减排补助政策</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">A.</strong>环保企业治理的相关技术让处理之后的污染物远低于标准，但是资金话费高，虽然有条文规定可以给予财政补助，企业却从来没有享受到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">B.</strong>国外的立法讲究立法成本，准备抓多少人、设多少监狱的经费，但是我国的立法没考虑执法成本，所以执行起来比较难。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">C.</strong>政策优惠在新环保法有规定，但是需要配套措施跟上，政府没有经费，上海有相关的计划，后续的政策和经费都在跟进，鼓励企业减排。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">3、关于第三方治理</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">A.</strong>以往大部分企业的项目上环保项目是应付式的，注重于建造，而不注重于运营，新环保法出来之后，企业环保治理更严格，未来可能出现一个园区只有一个环保企业来建设环保设施以及运营，环保局就跟这家环保企业进行对接，专业的事情交给专业的人员去做。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">B.</strong>政府是鼓励第三方治理的，但是企业需要有运营资质。如果出现排污超标，目前往往是找产生方负责，而不是治理方。关于第三方治理的责任关系等政府正在努力积极的研究。\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453909182', '0', '/uploads/17/article/0000000003.jpg', '');
INSERT INTO `tp_article` VALUES ('27', '2', '17', '中小型城镇生活垃圾未来方向', '10', '<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#C00000;\">啊啊啊11月沙龙概况</span></strong> <img src=\"/uploads/20161013\\ea34f715b787cbee731daa7a1e841043.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/uploads/20161013\\2e6b701a45a78d7d6a7c895f34f78690.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/uploads/20161013\\b6eff8aa22ccb4bd1e62d4f08dcccf64.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">沙龙主题：</strong>发掘中小型城镇环保商机—盐城\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">分享嘉宾：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;list-style-type:square;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			盐城市科学技术局高新技术及产业发展处处长 朱卫东\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			美国麻省理工学院CRMC负责人、国际固废资源化专家George Aronson\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			盐城市环保科技城招商局副局长、上海办事处主任 王军纯\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			天瑞仪器市场总监 陈兴跃\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">活动时间：</strong>11 月8 日，晚19:00-21:00\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">活动地点：</strong>江苏省盐城市迎宾馆2楼瑞鹤厅\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">主办单位：</strong>中国环博会  盐城市环保科技城\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">参与人数：</strong>65人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#C00000;\">|主题背景</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	全国各地打响了环境污染治理的号角，环保设施集中投入运营，目前一线城市环境治理设施建设已基本饱和，而中小城镇未来环境治理的空间仍较大。第三届中国ž盐城国际环保产业博览会在11月8日拉开帷幕，本次沙龙将借此平台，以“中小型城镇环保商机”为切入，邀请盐城市政府、市环保局、市科技局等相关领导，介绍盐城是环境治污的现状、困境；结合新环保法的实施，就建设项目管理、废弃处置、园区环境整治、饮用水源保护等环境治污需求进行分享讨论，同时还邀请到国际环保专业人士分享国际环保治理的相关经验和成果，并对如何走出中国特色的环保之路进行讨论。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#C00000;\">|主题分享</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">1、国家火炬计划盐城环保装备特色产业基地建设情况</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	盐城市科学技术局高新技术及产业发展处处长朱卫东首先从基地产业发展概况、基地企业发展情况、基地创新体系建设、基地运行的发展情况等四个方面介绍了盐城环保产业的大致情况。其中，对第四点基地运行发展情况提出更为详细的建议，朱卫东处长表示，首先要健全组织机构，只有在日渐完善的组织机构上，才能更全面更高效的服务基地的运行发展，其次，要科学发展规划，狠抓组织落实；最后提出强化政策交流促进产业升级的要求。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">2、Common Wealth</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	由来自美国麻省理工学院CRMC负责人、国际固废资源化专家George Aronson教授分享了美国在垃圾处理方面的过去与现状，并就垃圾处理方面的未来与沙龙成员进行了热烈的讨论。分享主要有以下几点：\r\n</p>\r\n<ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;list-style-type:lower-alpha;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			过去美国的垃圾处理以燃烧和填埋为主造，因此造成了大量的土地污染及废气排放，于是近代美国开始采取垃圾分类的办法对不同垃圾进行不同程度的处理，期望减少需要填埋及燃烧的垃圾的总量，并提高垃圾再利用的比例。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			直到1970年代，美国开始正视垃圾处理造成的污染，并对垃圾处理进行了进行立法，因而在1980至1990期间使垃圾处理行业得到了快速的成长。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			教授特别提到，美国在垃圾处理方面，采用依靠研究来建立标准的方式规范，并实现了筛选、回收、处理、填埋的成熟的垃圾处理流程。细致的分拣标准是对后续垃圾处理的最重要环节，经过分拣后，充分利用可再生的垃圾资源能大大降低垃圾处理的总量，从而减少垃圾处理产生的污染。通过完善垃圾处理设备，提高垃圾燃剂的燃烧程度，全面的改善垃圾处理所带来的污染。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"> 互动交流部分</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;list-style-type:square;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			有来宾就垃圾燃烧处理过程中产生的PM2.5及碳排放提出了疑问，教授也很坦然的表示，就目前美国的垃圾处理燃烧技术，PM2.5的排放量已经被控制在非常低的程度，但是碳排放是无法消除的，因此他们通过对燃烧炉及气体排放口过滤设备的特殊设计，尽力降低垃圾燃烧产生的碳排放问题，从而使垃圾燃烧的碳排放量保持在与天然气燃烧同等的程度上。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			来宾就垃圾处理中产生的剩余液问题提问，有趣的是教授表示在美国的垃圾处理中只有少量液体产生，只要在垃圾处理前进行晾晒及烘干基本就没有后续剩余液的问题。可见中国在垃圾处理上还是有着许多特有的问题，这也就需要我们的环保业者更加创新，更接地气，从而打造有中国特色的环保之路。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">3、中小型城镇的环保商机</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	由盐城市环保科技城招商局副局长、上海办事处主任的王军纯为沙龙的来宾介绍了盐城市环保科技城的概况，相关企业情况以及未来发展的方向，为有意来盐城寻找商机的于中小型企业做了一些很好的建议，同时王副局长还分享了盐城市环保科技城在设计建设初期的一些感受，特别提到国外专家关于低排放不代表零排放的观点，强调正视环境污染，未雨绸缪的环保理念。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">4、中国环保中小型企业未来发展之路</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"> </strong>天瑞仪器市场总监陈兴跃根据多年从事环保行业市场工作的经验与沙龙来宾分享了目前中国环保中小型企业的问题以及未来。\r\n</p>\r\n<ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 30px;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;list-style-type:lower-alpha;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			目前中国环保中小型企业都存在着商业模式单一的问题，不仅造成了盈利困难，也很大程度上局限了企业的发展。未来如何根据自身特殊调整商业模式是中小型环保企业的发展重点。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			从最新推出的环保法新政来看，未来对企业的污染监管及惩处力度将有很大程度的加强，对于中小型环保企业来说是一个前所未有的好时机。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;box-sizing:border-box !important;\">\r\n			把握大型城市污染转移的契机，将目光投向西南或江苏地区是不错的选择。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;color:#C00000;\">|现场观点碰撞</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">1. 中小型环保企业未来之路是否该追随大型城市污染转移的步伐？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">观点一：</strong>目前大型城市污染转移已经是普遍现象，将目光投向消化污染的二三线城市必然是中小型环保企业的发展之路。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">观点二：</strong>大型城市污染转移本身就是一种制度与政策的缺失，并非是解决污染的根本办法，未来政策可能会有所改变，因此应该用更加深远的眼光来选择未来发展的方向。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\" />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">2.关于生活垃圾未来的处理方向</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;white-space:normal;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;\">观点：</strong>来宾提出了关于蓝色经济的概念，蓝色经济是一种对人类与人类产生的垃圾的危机意识，是一种倡导如何将已经脱离大自然循环外的无法消化的垃圾重新定义，致力于建立对于所有垃圾的循环再生的概念。简单来说，未来在生产任何一件物品之前就需要规划出该物品完整的循环链，让垃圾的概念从根本上消失。\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '1453909213', '1453909276', '/uploads/17/article/0000000004.jpg', '');
